  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK516">
<l>ceyvāṉai nāṭi viṉaināṭik kālattō</l>
<l>ṭeyta vuṇarntu ceyal</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Let (a king) act, after having considered the agent (whom he is to employ), the deed (he desires to do), and the time which is suitable to it.</l>
            </lg>
